263
00:18:28,256 --> 00:18:29,258
Obrigado.

264
00:18:29,858 --> 00:18:32,635
Sr. Lomanitz. Vai ficar bem.

265
00:18:32,968 --> 00:18:33,968
Sr. Snyder.

266
00:18:34,678 --> 00:18:36,222
Agora, consideremos uma estrela.

267
